title: The Head of Medusa - George Brandt   (BBC 2013)
description:
The Head of Medusa by George Brandt

Benvenuto Cellini's `Perseus Holding the Head of Medusa' is one of the masterpieces of Renaissance sculpture.

Drawing on Cellini's colourful autobiography, the play reveals the dramatic story of its creation.

With Tim Pigott-Smith and Pamela Miles.

Director Sara Davies
